<svg class="tankan tankan-timeline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 783 205.5" width="783" height="205.5" role="img" aria-label="Timeline of Industrial Revolution" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14">
<style>
.tankan text { fill: #1f2328; }
